{"tid":1023754,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[童星] 谷花音大左變成咁既 🙄","createTime":"2019-02-16T04:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T07:57:09.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"299135b3b166f6474e8ba2443f7acee9058fd1c8","tid":1023754,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190215/large/1550232977_1d32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190215%2Flarge%2F1550232977_1d32.jpg&h=2500a2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190215/large/1550233019_7880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190215%2Flarge%2F1550233019_7880.jpg&h=74d35664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前睇日劇覺得佢幾得意，真係女大十八變？ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec64946d71290e19e6030e6ff9c294f3e866b3ac","tid":1023754,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得福仔同愛菜？<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png&h=d2164c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://d2dcan0armyq93.cloudfront.net/photo/odai/600/41da803eb59471f8cd1ccfe69d558899_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fd2dcan0armyq93.cloudfront.net%2Fphoto%2Fodai%2F600%2F41da803eb59471f8cd1ccfe69d558899_600.jpg&h=ee9cecb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/luckydog168/1312302230-061bd543e6984f5b105bc1fce6ed472f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fluckydog168%2F1312302230-061bd543e6984f5b105bc1fce6ed472f.jpg&h=d2bb2d34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://contents.oricon.co.jp/upimg/news/20130804/2027280_201308040554710001375577242c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.oricon.co.jp%2Fupimg%2Fnews%2F20130804%2F2027280_201308040554710001375577242c.jpg&h=a3f04122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家咁既樣 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/16/121751_ab038c092e63c373ecd6f1374ca0e8a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F16%2F121751_ab038c092e63c373ecd6f1374ca0e8a7.jpg&h=b51c6721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DzcTudgUYAAGWS_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDzcTudgUYAAGWS_.jpg&h=fdba131f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1476c4f2a3eace05ba060ca9185a679a789a7cae","tid":1023754,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/10/d10658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F10%2Fd10658.jpg&h=92b0197a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有大橋望美，不過佢前幾年退出左娛樂圈<br />\n<br />\n今年就20，唔知又變左咩樣 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c57e62a69e19a622a436283ae6a46258eb7a86af","tid":1023754,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"童星谷花音曾經在藝能界以可愛見稱，更被封為是「縮水版佐佐木希」，又跟新垣結衣、錦戶亮等不少紅星合作。<br />\n<br />\n不經不覺，谷花音已經14歲，由小妹妹長大成人，並已踏入少女階段，前日她在網誌上公開與諧星出川哲朗的合照，不過近照卻嚇親廣大網民，谷花音似乎隨住年紀增長，塊面亦越來越大，望落更十足一個大頭佛，與昔日的可愛樣好大出入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190215/large/1550233024_fc2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190215%2Flarge%2F1550233024_fc2b.jpg&h=357712bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76521a0165cbfdc283b63a9811bd4848e16cdd1a","tid":1023754,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:47:28.000Z","msg":"柒到"},{"pid":"eb37cb0371239e195d1a69bd2c1aa69b4bd01e2e","tid":1023754,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AKEHM397KX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAKEHM397KX0&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=8754ea5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AKEHM397KX0</a><br />\n<br />\n福仔同佢 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"323524154f92cfddb368ba52fac242d24f663b0e","tid":1023754,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柒到</blockquote><br />\n大面谷花 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2